So many people, however, according to the restaurant, would not all enter the restaurant together.
Similarly, the invoice issued in the summer of 2002 to the Jobb Jöv<0xC5><0x91>ért Foundation, later called Együtt in Harmadik Évezredért, is full of formal and content errors.
A pension of Badacsonytomaj has only three rooms, more than 10 people could not stay there, however on the invoice there were 130 guests.
